Package: ascii-stream
Version: 1.2.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Cheez-Noodlez1 <your-email@example.com>
Depends: python3, python3-pip, python3-pyqt6, python3-opencv, python3-numpy, python3-pygame, python3-requests, python3-selenium
Description: A retro-style application that converts video, HTML, and live websites into real-time ASCII art.
 This package provides the 'ascii-stream' command to view media in your terminal.
